projects.title: Project 1
projects.description:
This elegant black-and-white kitchen was completed in collaboration with DreamCabinets for Elite Home, a company known for building high-end modern homes. The property was sold immediately after being listed — a testament to the timeless design and attention to detail. The kitchen, all bedroom cabinets, interior doors, baseboards, and full millwork were designed and installed by StyleHomes and DreamCabinets. Together, we brought the designer’s vision to life, combining precision craftsmanship with modern aesthetics. Our portfolio includes full project photo sets — from kitchen and cabinets to doors, shelves, and all finishing details — so you can see the complete transformation of each home we’ve worked on. projects.title: Project 48
projects.description:
All restrooms at Father’s House Church — women’s, men’s, and children’s — were completely redesigned and rebuilt by several members of our church, including StyleHomes.
Each space was created as a custom project, combining functionality, cleanliness, and a modern aesthetic. The women’s restroom features a double sink with two height levels — one for adults and one for children — and a full-height mirror for convenience.
The men’s restroom carries the same thoughtful design, with warm wood accents, black fixtures, and marble-style walls.
The children’s restroom, located near the classrooms, was also designed individually to look bright, modern, and welcoming for kids. Every element was carefully planned — from easy maintenance to hidden plumbing — making each space both practical and elegant. Project completed by church members including StyleHomes Complete Restroom Renovation —
